    "description": "<blockquote><p>(Requires attunement by a Druid, Sorcerer, Warlock, or Wizard)</p></blockquote><p>While holding this staff you gain resistance to fire damage. You can use an action and expend charges to cast one of the following spells, using your spell save DC:</p><ul><li><p><em>burning hands</em> (1 charge)</p></li><li><p><em>fireball </em>(3 charges)</p></li><li><p><em>wall of fire</em> (4 charges)</p></li></ul><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p>The staff has 10 charges and regains 1d6+4 expended charges each dawn.</p><p>When the last charge is expended, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff crumbles to ash and is destroyed.</p>",
